{"tid":2048901,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黃耀明藍奕邦各自悼六四","createTime":"2020-06-03T05:59:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T16:38:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"47c7d93e8217a64c7a0fb6708cf2b6f30797b9f6","tid":2048901,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:59:26.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200603/IWBTAG6X6HJGZIUWFXURENHRFQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200603%2FIWBTAG6X6HJGZIUWFXURENHRFQ%2F&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=4c74bd68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200603%2FIWBTAG6X6HJGZIUWFXURENHRFQ%2F&h=dadd48ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200603/IWBTAG6X6HJGZIUWFXURENHRFQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n黃耀明藍奕邦各自悼六四<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7GKL44ANCNHKQEN342IH54WXRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7GKL44ANCNHKQEN342IH54WXRE.jpg&h=7f31f9b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每年都會出席六四燭光集會的黃耀明，留言嘲今年遭警方禁辦。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n明日是六四事件31周年，不過今年的六四燭光集會被警方以「限聚令」為由拒絕申請，以往均會出席集會的黃耀明（明哥）昨日在Ig貼出《蘋果》相關報道並留言：「就算沙士、狂風暴雨都未曾間斷嘅維園六四集會，今年被警方禁止舉辦。」藍奕邦亦在社交網貼「坦克人」相悼六四：「到咗今年，我真係好想po番呢張歷史意義極大嘅相，我驚過埋今年再冇機會。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S2CC5CA3JY7Z226YAHAH2AFRQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS2CC5CA3JY7Z226YAHAH2AFRQE.jpg&h=24e1fa00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳志森前晚在其個人頻道上跟網民探討美國與香港的警暴分別。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YAUOWRTWNSVJDJB6SD2HG3FCGQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYAUOWRTWNSVJDJB6SD2HG3FCGQ.jpg&h=c9657879&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藍奕邦昨日貼出「坦克」相片悼六四，坦言擔心以後再沒機會貼出來。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n至於吳志森前晚於其YouTube Channel中，跟網民探討美國警暴與香港警暴的分別，他指香港經歷過去一年，見到此等畫面真的會覺得匪夷所思：「警察竟然向示威者示弱？警察竟然同示威者行埋一齊？喺香港早已經革走咗九萬年啦。」比較完兩地後，吳志森表示雖然美國的暴動問題席捲全美，不過當地社會比香港多元化，故他有信心問題很快會平息，美國社會亦會很快復原。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：曹家誠"},{"pid":"87db60ef21acf54037aeb91803735cd8f2b9e200","tid":2048901,"uid":83328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:00:04.000Z","msg":"黃奕邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd5c03cdd0dc58ccef5db376549c58aa7119751","tid":2048901,"uid":236538,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6JwuYGD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6JwuYGD.jpg&h=0cfad5c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81680a66f297184880f57c7fe6c0f6a9d2e4eb7f","tid":2048901,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbd5c03cdd0dc58ccef5db376549c58aa7119751","tid":2048901,"uid":236538,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6JwuYGD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6JwuYGD.jpg&h=0cfad5c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T16:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}